description: The Samson’s truck is serving up the wonderful 9” wieners that have been winning over every type of North Texas eater (vegan, vegetarian, gluten-free) for years!You’ve just gotta try their tasty selection of top-quality dogs, including the Texan (Samson’s Dog with Beef Chili, Sharp Cheddar, and Onions), the South West (with Green Chile Chicken Chili, Cilantro, Feta, Onions), the Vegetation (Veggie Dog with Veggie Chili, Asian Slaw, Jalapeños)For all this and more, come on out to Samson’s, get your hot dog fix on, let your hair down, and have some crazy-tasty fun.
name: Samson's Gourmet Hot Dogs
